86
00:15:04,780 --> 00:15:06,190
Mother.

87
00:15:15,690 --> 00:15:16,720
Mother.

88
00:15:22,850 --> 00:15:23,900
Xun.

89
00:15:25,230 --> 00:15:26,920
You must survive

90
