168
00:26:13,160 --> 00:26:14,100
Zhao Xifeng

169
00:26:14,100 --> 00:26:16,340
killed his pregnant sister.

170
00:26:16,740 --> 00:26:19,730
Yuwen Huai beheaded Yan Shicheng.

171
00:26:19,730 --> 00:26:20,900
Those people

172
00:26:21,590 --> 00:26:23,540
want Yan Xun dead

173
00:26:23,540 --> 00:26:25,790
more than we do.

174
00:26:26,800 --> 00:26:28,830
But the head of Imperial Prison

175
00:26:29,380 --> 00:26:30,750
