176
00:26:31,070 --> 00:26:32,220
He and Marquis Dingbei

177
00:26:32,220 --> 00:26:33,680
go way back.

178
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:35,710
Isn’t his youngest son

179
00:26:35,710 --> 00:26:38,240
