232
00:29:49,320 --> 00:29:50,930
Help me shower and get dressed,

233
00:29:51,330 --> 00:29:52,600
and prepare a carriage for me.

234
00:29:53,440 --> 00:29:54,430
I’m going out.

235
00:29:55,040 --> 00:29:55,870
Your Highness,

236
00:29:55,870 --> 00:29:57,290
