237
00:30:03,340 --> 00:30:04,880
Qingshan House of Yuwen.

238
00:30:05,450 --> 00:30:06,730
I need to see Yuwen Yue.

239
00:30:09,900 --> 00:30:12,180
Your Highness, Master Yuwen Yue

240
00:30:12,180 --> 00:30:12,990
from Qingshan House

241
00:30:12,990 --> 00:30:14,250
