242
00:30:18,120 --> 00:30:19,440
The Zhaos and Weis

243
00:30:19,440 --> 00:30:21,110
have planned everything well.

244
00:30:21,800 --> 00:30:24,080
But that may only
be their wishful thinking.

245
00:30:26,040 --> 00:30:27,520
Yuwen Yue has already sent people

246
00:30:27,520 --> 00:30:28,840
to protect

247
00:30:28,840 --> 00:30:30,200
Luo Yongchen’s family.

248
00:30:30,850 --> 00:30:32,720
Half of Qingshan House’s men

249
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:33,870
are at Luo’s.

250
00:30:34,640 --> 00:30:36,690
And the youngest son of Luo Yongchen

251
00:30:36,690 --> 00:30:37,800
has been grounded.

252
00:30:38,590 --> 00:30:39,990
If they’re trying to

253
00:30:39,990 --> 00:30:40,890
work from that angle,

254
00:30:42,230 --> 00:30:44,190
