00:30:47,300 --> 00:30:49,290
They fear to make a big fuss.

257
00:30:49,570 --> 00:30:50,850
We don’t.

258
00:30:55,860 --> 00:30:56,940
We can

259
00:30:58,050 --> 00:31:00,020
