made it public?

290
00:33:01,200 --> 00:33:01,940
You have a point.

291
00:33:02,500 --> 00:33:04,060
Except for you,

292
00:33:04,440 --> 00:33:06,060
I don’t know who I can trust.

293
00:33:06,960 --> 00:33:08,910
So just get to the point.

294
00:33:45,890 --> 00:33:46,630
Miss.

295
00:33:56,800 --> 00:33:57,490
Yes?

296
00:33:57,490 --> 00:33:59,290
Is His Excellency getting better?

297
00:34:01,770 --> 00:34:02,590
Who are you?

298
00:34:03,450 --> 00:34:04,930
I work under Mr. Luo.

299
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:06,990
Mr. Luo is Marquis Dingbei’s best friend,

300
00:34:07,190 --> 00:34:09,140
and he is in charge of this prison.

301
00:34:11,050 --> 00:34:12,200
He has been seriously injured,

302
00:34:12,490 --> 00:34:13,730
and he needs clean water, food,

303
00:34:13,730 --> 00:34:14,490
medicine

304
00:34:14,490 --> 00:34:15,470
and a physician.

305
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:16,820
You know

306
00:34:16,960 --> 00:34:18,170
it’s dangerous

307
00:34:18,170 --> 00:34:19,150
to bring anyone in.

308
00:34:19,150 --> 00:34:20,700
Look, Miss,

309
00:34:21,240 --> 00:34:22,620
I have got some hot porridge.

310
00:34:23,330 --> 00:34:25,310
You can feed it to His Excellency.

311
00:34:25,310 --> 00:34:26,620
As for hot water and medicine,

312
00:34:26,730 --> 00:34:28,210
I will get them prepared later.

313
00:34:28,430 --> 00:34:28,960
Here you go.

314
00:34:30,470 --> 00:34:31,470
Eat it while it’s hot.

315
00:34:31,940 --> 00:34:32,700
Thank you.

316
00:34:32,970 --> 00:34:33,580
You’re welcome.

317
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:23,970
You are a clever girl.

318
00:35:24,600 --> 00:35:25,780
What a shame!

319
00:35:26,020 --> 00:35:26,790
You two

320
00:35:26,940 --> 00:35:28,240
could’ve died

321
00:35:28,240 --> 00:35:29,020
a painless death.

322
00:35:29,020 --> 00:35:30,180
Who sent you here?

323
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:31,800
Does it matter?

324
00:35:32,470 --> 00:35:33,540
You know

325
00:35:33,540 --> 00:35:35,270
many out there want you dead.

326
00:35:35,560 --> 00:35:36,940
One more won’t make a difference.

327
00:35:37,740 --> 00:35:40,020
Do yourself a favor
and end your suffering.

328
00:35:40,780 --> 00:35:41,330
Come on.

329
00:35:42,470 --> 00:35:44,100
Let me give you a hand.

330
00:35:44,320 --> 00:35:45,990
The way you act shows

331
00:35:45,990 --> 00:35:47,550
you aren’t an official, right?

332
00:35:49,690 --> 00:35:50,760
You are from the underworld.

333
00:35:52,900 --> 00:35:54,580
If so,

334
00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:56,530
you must be familiar with the Storm Token.

335
00:35:58,290 --> 00:35:59,570
How did you know the Token?

336
00:36:01,730 --> 00:36:03,430
Speak! What’s your connection

337
00:36:03,430 --> 00:36:04,830
with the Storm Token?

338
00:36:06,010 --> 00:36:07,810
Aren’t you just a maid?

339
00:36:09,100 --> 00:36:09,920
Were I

340
00:36:09,920 --> 00:36:11,000
just a menial,

341
00:36:11,300 --> 00:36:12,360
how could I survive

342
00:36:12,360 --> 00:36:13,190
to this day?

343
00:36:15,140 --> 00:36:16,190
Who are you?

344
00:36:17,370 --> 00:36:18,820
My identity doesn’t matter.

345
00:36:18,950 --> 00:36:19,540
What matters is

346
00:36:19,540 --> 00:36:20,890
that I know where the Storm Token is.

347
00:36:21,160 --> 00:36:21,870
Where is it?

348
00:36:25,310 --> 00:36:26,990
What do you want?

349
00:36:29,310 --> 00:36:30,810
Get me out of here.

350
00:36:31,010 --> 00:36:32,040
You should know

351
00:36:32,460 --> 00:36:34,460
there are traps everywhere.

352
00:36:35,240 --> 00:36:36,980
Everyone wants him dead.

353
00:36:36,980 --> 00:36:39,390
I can’t get you guys out.

354
00:36:39,790 --> 00:36:41,540
Not him, just me.

355
00:36:42,080 --> 00:36:43,370
Are you leaving him behind?

356
00:36:43,490 --> 00:36:45,090
We aren’t related by blood.

357
00:36:45,240 --> 00:36:46,940
Why should I die with him?

358
00:36:47,400 --> 00:36:48,270
That makes sense.

359
00:36:48,530 --> 00:36:50,690
But how should I know

360
00:36:50,690 --> 00:36:51,510
what you said is true?

361
00:36:57,600 --> 00:36:59,220
I have proof, of course.

362
00:36:59,220 --> 00:37:00,090
What is it?

363
00:37:31,640 --> 00:37:33,700
Storm Token is a nice bait.

364
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:35,390
If you want it,

365
00:37:38,620 --> 00:37:40,180
go seize it in hell.

366
00:37:46,970 --> 00:37:47,660
My lady,

367
00:37:48,790 --> 00:37:49,990
Shadow made it.

368
00:37:50,730 --> 00:37:51,850
Luo Yongchen is dead.

369
00:37:53,650 --> 00:37:54,640
Where is Shadow?

370
00:37:55,570 --> 00:37:56,910
He hasn’t come back yet.

371
00:37:57,540 --> 00:37:58,650
Our men saw

372
00:37:58,650 --> 00:38:00,150
Luo’s servant

373
00:38:00,150 --> 00:38:02,060
go home in haste to report,

374
00:38:02,360 --> 00:38:03,790
and found out what happened.

375
00:38:12,870 --> 00:38:14,010
Shadow always

376
00:38:14,010 --> 00:38:15,530
aims high

377
00:38:15,720 --> 00:38:17,120
and thinks highly of himself.

378
00:38:17,690 --> 00:38:18,670
I’m afraid

379
00:38:19,870 --> 00:38:21,190
he’s going straight

380
00:38:21,190 --> 00:38:22,200
to kill Yan Xun.

381
00:38:22,970 --> 00:38:24,210
Would he?

382
00:38:25,810 --> 00:38:27,310
You only sent him

383
00:38:27,310 --> 00:38:28,550
to kill Luo Yongchen.

384
00:38:30,150 --> 00:38:31,810
These people of the underworld

385
00:38:32,460 --> 00:38:33,580
aren’t technically

386
00:38:33,580 --> 00:38:35,480
obedient.

387
00:38:36,640 --> 00:38:37,920
Alright. Forget about him.

388
00:38:45,670 --> 00:38:46,670
My Lady,

389
00:38:47,030 --> 00:38:48,480
a message just came

390
00:38:48,660 --> 00:38:49,740
saying that Shadow was killed

391
00:38:49,740 --> 00:38:50,830
by that maid with Yan Xun.

392
00:38:51,310 --> 00:38:52,630
She said to Shadow

393
00:38:52,630 --> 00:38:54,190
that she knew where the Storm Token is.

394
00:38:58,780 --> 00:39:01,160
Will this work?

395
00:39:02,910 --> 00:39:05,430
Do our best and leave the rest to heaven.

396
00:39:06,230 --> 00:39:07,350
The result

397
00:39:08,390 --> 00:39:09,530
is out of our control.

398
00:39:15,350 --> 00:39:16,280
Young Master Yue.

399
00:39:16,750 --> 00:39:17,560
Young Master Yue.

400
00:39:18,010 --> 00:39:19,230
Mr. Luo was killed.

401
00:39:30,310 --> 00:39:31,080
Really?

402
00:39:31,080 --> 00:39:31,850
Yes.

403
00:39:32,160 --> 00:39:33,020
The man who gave the obituary notice

404
00:39:33,020 --> 00:39:34,490
is at the state office of Chang’an.

405
00:39:39,390 --> 00:39:41,210
Clearly, heaven is on my side.

406
00:39:42,440 --> 00:39:43,200
Yan Xun,

407
00:39:45,380 --> 00:39:46,860
I can imagine how painful you feel.

408
00:39:48,170 --> 00:39:49,830
Do you want to die

409
00:39:50,880 --> 00:39:53,700
to end all your suffering
once and for all?

410
00:39:55,490 --> 00:39:56,750
Dying is easy.

411
00:39:59,170 --> 00:40:00,330
You’d have no pain

412
00:40:01,550 --> 00:40:02,770
or hatred.

413
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:05,940
It’s just like taking a nap.

414
00:40:08,080 --> 00:40:09,310
In your dream,

415
00:40:10,120 --> 00:40:10,960
you are still

416
00:40:10,960 --> 00:40:12,440
that high and mighty prince.

417
00:40:15,280 --> 00:40:18,250
Your parents and siblings are still alive.

418
00:40:19,290 --> 00:40:20,310
How wonderful!

419
00:40:22,830 --> 00:40:24,470
Death is always the easiest.

420
00:40:26,280 --> 00:40:26,990
What is really hard

421
00:40:29,270 --> 00:40:33,190
is batting the thought of death to live.

422
00:40:35,420 --> 00:40:36,320
Yan Xun.

423
00:40:36,630 --> 00:40:38,300
I have nothing at all.

424
00:40:38,920 --> 00:40:40,190
I don’t even know

425
00:40:40,190 --> 00:40:41,470
where my birth parents are.

426
00:40:42,530 --> 00:40:45,410
People who were nice to me are all dead.

427
00:40:48,850 --> 00:40:51,880
Some took a hit for others

428
00:40:53,070 --> 00:40:54,520
and died tragically.

429
00:40:55,620 --> 00:40:58,420
Some were raped to death

430
00:40:59,660 --> 00:41:01,800
and tossed among mass graves

431
00:41:03,160 --> 00:41:04,910
like a pile of trash.

432
00:41:08,400 --> 00:41:10,220
The world is supposed to be fair.

433
00:41:11,280 --> 00:41:12,670
Even maids

434
00:41:13,110 --> 00:41:14,790
should have the right to live.

435
00:41:18,110 --> 00:41:18,750
I couldn’t understand

436
00:41:18,750 --> 00:41:19,930
why people

437
00:41:21,280 --> 00:41:22,050
are divided into separate classes

438
00:41:22,050 --> 00:41:23,470
when they are born into this world.

439
00:41:25,160 --> 00:41:26,560
Why rabbits are doomed to be wolves’ prey?

440
00:41:26,560 --> 00:41:27,770
Why can’t they

441
00:41:27,770 --> 00:41:28,620
fight back?

442
00:41:30,290 --> 00:41:31,720
But now, I know.

443
00:41:32,820 --> 00:41:34,710
That’s because rabbits
are not strong enough.

444
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:39,510
If you don’t want to be looked down,

445
00:41:40,830 --> 00:41:42,280
you have to stand up first.

446
00:41:43,600 --> 00:41:44,410
Yan Xun.

447
00:41:46,020 --> 00:41:47,660
Right now, I’m still weak

448
00:41:49,470 --> 00:41:51,130
but I’m patient.

449
00:41:52,090 --> 00:41:53,290
I still have enough time.

450
00:41:55,890 --> 00:41:57,230
Those people who owed me

451
00:41:59,880 --> 00:42:01,400
will not get away with it.

452
00:42:08,480 --> 00:42:10,190
I will watch them

453
00:42:10,430 --> 00:42:12,150
pay the price for what they did

454
00:42:12,570 --> 00:42:13,920
eventually.

455
00:42:16,480 --> 00:42:19,670
Otherwise, even if I die,

456
00:42:20,870 --> 00:42:22,170
I will turn in my grave.

457
00:42:28,640 --> 00:42:29,460
Yan Xun.

458
00:42:30,930 --> 00:42:31,960
Do you remember

459
00:42:31,960 --> 00:42:32,510
your mother’s last words

460
00:42:32,510 --> 00:42:33,770
to you?

461
00:42:40,400 --> 00:42:42,250
She wanted you to live well.

462
00:42:42,980 --> 00:42:44,550
However low you have to bend,

463
00:42:45,740 --> 00:42:47,430
you must go on with your life.

464
00:42:47,430 --> 00:42:48,760
Because you still have

465
00:42:48,760 --> 00:42:49,390
tons of unfulfilled missions.

466
00:42:52,480 --> 00:42:53,870
Do you know what they are?

467
00:42:54,480 --> 00:42:55,960
Lower your hand and swallow your pride.

468
00:42:56,170 --> 00:42:57,590
Endure the hardships

469
00:42:58,380 --> 00:42:59,790
and wait for the right time to come

470
00:43:01,170 --> 00:43:02,160
to kill all those people

471
00:43:02,160 --> 00:43:03,390
who murdered your family

472
00:43:03,390 --> 00:43:04,610
on your own,

473
00:43:04,980 --> 00:43:06,240
and avenge their deaths.

474
00:43:08,140 --> 00:43:10,170
They have high hopes in you.

475
00:43:11,590 --> 00:43:12,540
They’re watching you

476
00:43:12,540 --> 00:43:13,940
up there.

477
00:43:16,210 --> 00:43:17,790
Are you going to let them down?

478
00:43:19,020 --> 00:43:19,840
Are you going to

479
00:43:19,840 --> 00:43:20,870
leave them there unavenged?

480
00:43:22,430 --> 00:43:23,800
Are you going to watch them

481
00:43:23,800 --> 00:43:25,200
ruin your father’s legacy?

482
00:43:28,060 --> 00:43:29,100
Are you

483
00:43:30,420 --> 00:43:32,030
willing to rot

484
00:43:32,850 --> 00:43:34,320
in this disgusting cage

485
00:43:34,790 --> 00:43:36,350
like a coward?

486
00:43:37,650 --> 00:43:38,870
Are you?

